    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A super-absorbent polymer, the sodium salt of polyacrylic acid, with broad commercial applications. In a conservation context, it is used as a moisture buffer material for humidity control in museum exhibit cases and in historic structures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
